            "notes": "This deck focuses on utilizing aggressive creatures and powerful spells to quickly overwhelm opponents in a one-on-one duel commander game. The deck includes a variety of mana-producing creatures such as Birds of Paradise and Elvish Mystic, allowing for a fast start and quick ramping into bigger threats like Avenger of Zendikar and Maelstrom Wanderer. With a mix of removal spells like Fatal Push and Swords to Plowshares, along with disruptive creatures like Goblin Cratermaker and Shriekmaw, the deck aims to control the board while also maintaining a steady stream of threats. The inclusion of powerful cards like Demonic Tutor and Omnath, Locus of Creation ensure that the deck has plenty of ways to close out the game efficiently."
